title: California Firm Recalls Meat and Poultry Products Produced Without Benefit of Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, Feb. 15, 2012 - AA Meat Products Corporation, a Maywood, Calif. establishment, is recalling an undetermined amount of meat and poultry products because they may have been produced without the benefit of federal inspection, the U.S. Department of Agriculture's Food Safety and Inspection Service...
